-----------------------
What is Anna-Readonly
-----------------------
Make it easy to view Web forms unless user wants to edit it.

-----------------------
How to use
-----------------------
In HTML->HEAD, you need to add Jquery and jquery tools (for tooltip) as shown below.
		<script src="jquery-1.6.2.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
		<script src="jquery.tools.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
		<script src="anna-readonly.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
		<style>
		.tooltip {
			display:none;
			background-color:#ffa;
			border:1px solid #cc9;
			padding:5px;
			font-size:13px;
			-moz-box-shadow: 2px 2px 11px #666;
			-webkit-box-shadow: 2px 2px 11px #666;
		}

